N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 150.5 - Duplicate receipts

State Regulations

The department shall not issue duplicate receipts except on
satisfactory evidence that the original was never received. A request for a
duplicate receipt must be made within three months of the date of the receipted
transaction. All duplicate receipts will be annotated as
such. Notes
